            <h1 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-4">Arsenal Vault Desktop vs Cloud: Which Is Right for You?</h1>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-6">Both versions have the same features. The difference is where your data lives and how you access it. Here's how to decide.</p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-400">
                <span><i class="bi bi-calendar3 mr-1"></i> March 27, 2026</span>
